message.p:
In a template text, a $${var} indicates a place holder
named var which is substituted with a widget or string
that is bound to that variable. Other syntactical constructs are:

  arguments
  $${var arg1 arg2}
  conditions
  $${<condition>} ...
  $${</condition>}

  functions
  $${fun:arg1 arg2}

