message.p:
The following table gives an overview of properties that can be
directly modified from C++.





      Class
      Property
      Description





      ${doc-link WWidget}
      setPositionScheme()
      CSS position property.



      ${doc-link WWidget}
      setOffsets()
      CSS top, right, bottom, left properties.



      ${doc-link WWidget}
      resize()
      CSS width, height properties.



      ${doc-link WWidget}
      setMinimumSize()
      CSS min-width, min-height properties.



      ${doc-link WWidget}
      setMaximumSize()
      CSS max-width, max-height properties.



      ${doc-link WWidget}
      setLineHeight()
      CSS line-height property.



      ${doc-link WWidget}
      setFloatSide()
      CSS float property.



      ${doc-link WWidget}
      setClearSides()
      CSS clear property.



      ${doc-link WWidget}
      setMargin()
      CSS margin property.



      ${doc-link WWidget}
      setVerticalAlignment()
      CSS vertical-align property.



      ${doc-link WWidget}
      setInline(), setHidden()
      CSS display property.



      ${doc-link WCssDecorationStyle}
      setCursor()
      CSS cursor property.



      ${doc-link WCssDecorationStyle}
      setBackgroundColor(), setBackgroundImage()
      CSS background property.



      ${doc-link WCssDecorationStyle}
      setForegroundColor()
      CSS color property.



      ${doc-link WCssDecorationStyle}
      setBorder()
      CSS border property.



      ${doc-link WCssDecorationStyle}
      setFont()
      CSS font property.



      ${doc-link WCssDecorationStyle}
      setTextDecoration()
      CSS text-decoration property.

